race.description: Asian United Food Service Dash Division1
race.comment: NORA'S BOY (7) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 312m (18.39). Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and nine minor placings to his name from 15 starts. Worth another chance. SYDNEY SURCHARGE (8) has a strong record this trip with seven wins and six placings from 21 starts. Recorded a 2 length win (22.14) in a Free For All last time at this track. Looks one of the chances. HERE COMES BLUE (2) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (22.48) but did record best time of the card when winning three back. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than last start and can bounce back. ZELDA CHAOS (5) has a solid strike rate at this distance.
